      <p>Contract & consulting in payments/security/backend.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="aside-card accent">
      <div class="card-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Remote first</h3>
      <p>Async-friendly. Time zones aren't a problem if the work matters.</p>
    </div>
